        "primary": {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "When Scent Becomes Art",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "At Dubai Design Week, Hind Al-Oud presented an immersive pop-up installation that transformed fragrance into art and poetry into space. Inspired by Kibriya’E by poet Faisal Al-Adwani, the activation introduced two exclusive perfumes — Alifi and Ya’E — expressed as a multi-sensory journey from certainty to singularity, blending scent, light, sound, and spatial storytelling into an evocative design experience.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
        },
        "items": []
